<span onclick="ElideText('Publications')" class="sectionheader">
  Select Publications
</span>
<div id="Publications" style="display:visible" class="sectionbody">
  
<ol>

<li>
S. Rivera P., Z. Fei, and J. Griffioen, Providing a High Level Abstraction for SDN Networks,
International Workshop on Computer and Networking Experimental Research using Testbeds
(CNERT 2015), June 2015.
</li>


<li>
X. Chen, T. Wolf, J. Griffioen, O. Ascigil, R. Dutta, G. Rouskas, S. Bhat, I. Baldine, and K.
Calvert, Design of a Protocol to Enable Economic Transactions for Network Services, IEEE
International Conference on Communications 2015 (ICC 2015) - Next Generation Networking
Symposium, June 2015.
</li>

<li>
T. Wolf, J. Griffioen, K. Calvert, R. Dutta, G. Rouskas, I. Baldin, and A. Nagurney,
ChoiceNet: Toward an Economy Plane for the Internet, Computer Communication Review, pp 58-65, Vol
44, No 3, July 2014.
</li>

<li>
S. Huang, J. Griffioen, and K. Calvert, Network Hypervisors: Enhancing SDN Infrastructure,
Computer Communications, Elsevier Publishers, pp 87-96, Vol 46, No 15, June 2014.
</li>

<li>
J. Griffioen, Z. Fei, H. Nasir, X. Wu, J. Reed, and C. Carpenter, Measuring Experiments
in GENI, Computer Networks, Elsevier Publishers, pp 17-32, Vol 63, April 2014.
</li>


<li>
X. Wu and J. Griffioen, Supporting Application-based Route Selection
International Conference on Computer Communication Networks 2014 (ICCCN
2014), Communication Architectures,  
Algorithms, Measurement and Performance Evaluation (CAAME), August 2014.
</li>

<li>
O. Ascigil, K. Calvert, and J. Griffioen, On the Scalability of Interdomain Path Computations,
IFIP Networking 2014 Conference, June 2014.
</li>

<li>
S. Huang and J. Griffioen, Network Hypervisors: Managing the Emerging SDN Chaos,
International Conference on Computer Communication Networks 2013 (ICCCN 2013), Network
Architectures and Clean-Slate Designs (NACSD), July 2013.
</li>

<li>
T. Wolf, J. Griffioen, K. Calvert, R. Dutta, G. Rouskas, I. Baldine, and A. Nagurney, Choice
as a Principle in Network Architecture, Short paper appearing in the poster proceedings of
the ACM SIGCOMM 2012 Conference, August 2012.
</li>

<li>
S. Yuan, O. Ascigil, J. Griffioen, and K. Calvert, Leveraging Legacy Software
in Clean-Slate Network Architectures, International Conference on Computer
Communication Networks 2012 (ICCCN 2012), Network Architectures and
Clean-Slate Designs (NACSD), July 2012.
</li>
  
